title: 2nd annual NFL schedule bonanza
itunes:title: 2nd annual NFL schedule bonanza
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- delve into the 2015 NFL schedule (10:40), highlighting Week 1's marquee matchups and debating which teams got a lucky draw (20:45). Plus, grading the primetime games (31:37), a look at the Thanksgiving Day slate and much more.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
